        {
          "title": "Elastic Cluster Compute (on-demand vCPU pricing)",
          "helpText": "On-Demand vCPUs let you pay per second, with no long-term commitments or upfront fees. This frees you from the cost and complexity of planning and purchasing database capacity in advance, and from having to guess the correct capacity. Pricing is per vCPU hour consumed, from the time your Amazon DocumentDB Elastic Clusters is launched until it is deleted. vCPUs provide RAM (memory), I/O operations, and the required CPU cores for your workload. Partial vCPU hours are billed in one-second increments, with a 10-minute charge following a billable status change such as creating, modifying, or deleting your cluster. ",
          "expandable": true,
          "defaultExpansion": false,
          "helpUrl": {
            "$LINK": {
              "type": "pricing",
              "path": "/documentdb/pricing/"
            }
          },
